{"bgColorIndex":0,"note":"Skills\n- Kubernetes\/Docker\n- Terraform \n- Python\n- AWS (cloud security)\n- xml\n- bash\n- c++\n- Networking\n- AI\/ML\n- APIs\n\n\nNew Roles (we are moving from Security Engineers to Security System Designers)\n1. AI Red Teamer\n2. AI Security Orchestrator\n3. AI Governance\n4. AI Threat Modeler\n\nStart thinking: “I design systems that perform security reviews automatically”\n\nFocus moves from\n- finding issues -> Designing systems that prevent them\n- running tools -> Orchestrating intelligent workflows\n- manual checks -> Continuous enforcement\n","textColorIndex":1}